<item>
            <title>[PIG-3801] Auto local mode does not call storeSchema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3801</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/pig/blob/trunk/src/org/apache/pig/backend/hadoop/executionengine/mapReduceLayer/MapReduceLauncher.java#L481&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/pig/blob/trunk/src/org/apache/pig/backend/hadoop/executionengine/mapReduceLayer/MapReduceLauncher.java#L481&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pig code explicitly runs PigOutputCommitter.storeCleanup for local jobs. We also need to add this for auto-local jobs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To repro this problem, run-&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;  a = load &apos;2.txt&apos; as (a0:chararray, a1:int);&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;  store a into &apos;a&apos; using PigStorage(&apos;,&apos;,&apos;-schema&apos;);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This creates .pig_schema file in pig -x local mode, but does not create .pig_schema file in auto-local mode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
